{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d40e1b654","title":"七绝·贾谊","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"94a31a917a","index":0,"year":1964,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"8d40e1b654"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"639bfabde6","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"8d40e1b654","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贾生才调世无伦，本句借用李商隐《贾生》句：“贾生才调更无伦。”贾生，指费谊（前200—前168），西汉洛阳（今河南洛阳东）人，时称贾生，西汉政论家、文学家。初被汉文帝召为博士，不久迁为太中大夫。文帝想任他为公卿，因遭大臣周勃、灌婴等排挤，姬为长沙王太傅。才调，指才气、才能。"},{"id":"792bd1fa1e","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"8d40e1b654","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"吊屈文，贾谊吸为长沙王太傅后，渡湘江时有感于屈原忠而见疏，作《吊屈原赋》，“因以自喻”。"},{"id":"e47352b93c","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"8d40e1b654","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"梁王单马寻常事，何用衰伤付一生，贾谊后被征拜为梁怀王太傅，因梁怀王重马而死，他认为自己“为傅无状”，优郁自伤，不久去世。毛泽东非常赞赏费谊的才华，认为他因袁伤而死不值得，并感到很悦情。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6aebb1d1df","type":"title","text":"七绝·费谊","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"8d40e1b654"},{"id":"639bfabde6","type":"paragraph","text":"贾生才调世无伦，哭泣情怀吊屈文问。梁王望马寻常事，何用衰伤付一生。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"8d40e1b654"}],"page":{"id":"7e115fa36f","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"8d40e1b654","start":412,"end":412}}}},"__N_SSG":true}